      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014seriously, it's pristine! If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
