    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity. This S54 powerplant features a recently overhauled Double VANOS system and verified subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary stress points. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, utilizing refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers for a balanced lateral load distribution. Compression and leak-down tests confirm optimal cylinder wall integrity and valve seating. This is a turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
