    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage, and it shows. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, having been treated with a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating that produces a deep, mirror-like reflection with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is firm with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every toggle, screen, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. I possess a complete, chronological service history binder documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed by master technicians. The engine bay is pristine, the undercarriage is free of oxidation, and it sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires with zero curb rash on the alloy wheels. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
      "price": 48500.0,
